  <brief_title>Natural History of Hepatitis C in Patients With Normal Liver Tests</brief_title>
  <official_title>Determinants of Disease Severity in Patients With Chronic Hepatitis C and Normal Serum Aminotransferases (Normal Liver Tests)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
